Class LibraryItem

java.lang.Object
LibraryItem
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<LibraryItem>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Book, MusicCD
public class LibraryItem extends Object implements Comparable<LibraryItem>, Serializable
LibraryItem is an abstract base class representing a generic item in the library. It implements Comparable to allow sorting by title and Serializable for persistence.
